parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic throttle control system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the traction control warning light and electrical system warning light are illuminated
the vehicle will not restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the cruise control system can cause the vehicle to lose speed control, leading to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The cruise control system will not turn on
the cruise control system will not disengage
the vehicle speed will not match the set speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery saver mode warning indicator is illuminated
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the vehicle will not restart.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause various systems to fail, leading to accidents or loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: The dashboard cluster goes out
the radio and console go black
the vehicle will not turn on
the alarm system will not work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the clutch pedal can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the air conditioning system can cause discomfort and distraction to the driver, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The air conditioning system blows cold air when set to heat
the air conditioning system does not work until the vehicle is turned off and restarted.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the backup camera can cause accidents or injuries while reversing.
symptoms: The backup camera screen is black
the backup camera image is flipped
the backup camera was previously repaired but the problem persists.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the power steering system can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The service power steering warning indicator is illuminated
the power steering system fails to operate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate headlight illumination can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially when driving at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The headlights provide no side illumination
the light projected into the front direction does not give total coverage
the headlights are too dim
the high beams do not illuminate anything on the sides of the car
the headlights do not shine at the sides
making it difficult to see when turning
especially on dark roads or rural areas.
